What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Coated Fabrics Market?

Analysis and Insights :

Global Coated Fabrics Market

The coated fabrics market is estimated to reach a value of USD 36.96 billion by 2028 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 4.65% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on coated fabrics market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth.

Coated fabrics are the type of fabrics which are covered, coated or treated with various substances such as rubber, varnish, lacquer and thermoplastic coatings so as to make the material last longer and be resistant to dust, water, oil and other liquids. These coated fabrics are produced from smooth and pile fabrics and are sometimes combined with porolon to make them soft.

The increase in safety measures in the transportation application is likely to influence the growth of the coated fabrics market. In line with this, the strict regulatory requirements for workers’ safety driving the protective clothing segment is also expected to act as a key determinant which will favor the growth of the coated fabrics market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Furthermore, the rapid technological innovations aimed at the lessening of raw material prices and achieving faster and efficient production and rapid industrialization coupled with infrastructure development are also expected to positively impact the growth of the coated fabrics market. The major factor which is expected to forward the growth of the market is the rapid increase in the investment in construction and infrastructure, oil and gas, automotive, chemical and manufacturing industries associated with notable economic development.

However, the fluctuating raw material prices, rise in environmental concerns and easy availability of substitutes are expected to act as key restraint towards coated fabrics market growth rate in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Whereas, the disposal or recycling of waste and lack of safety compliance are expected to challenge the growth of the coated fabrics market in the above mentioned forecast period.

Furthermore, the rapid industrialization in emerging economies and innovative product development in the protective clothing segment will further offer a variety of growth opportunities for the coated fabrics market in the above mentioned forecast period.

